snippet.title: Army-police Conducts Mock Drill at Pathankot to Deal with Terror Attacks

localized.description:
Army and police jointly conducts mock drill at Pathankot to deal with terror attacks. In this mock drill two terrorists capture alive while two killed on the spot.
